title: New In Chess Magazine 1985-2015
description:
New In Chess has regular contributions from all the world's best players. Magnus Carlsen, Vladimir Kramnik, Levon Aronian, Vishy Anand, Sergey Karjakin, Hikaru Nakamura, Veselin Topalov, Fabiano Caruana, Alexander Grischuk, Hou Yifan, Judit Polgar. You name them, we have them. Perhaps that's why New In Chess is also their favourite chess magazine!

8 issues a year
800 pages a year of the very best in chess
on-the-spot tournament reports
columns both serious and hilarious
in-depth interviews
'Secrets of Opening Surprises'
chess history that comes to life
endgames and studies
chess anecdotes and curiosities
great pictures and drawings
an honest GM opinion on the latest chess books
exclusive columns by Anish Giri and Nigel Short
games analysed by the top players themselves
